Colin Wescott

Summary

I am a Performance Analyst currently working at the Cronulla Sharks. I joined the club for the 2023 season as a Performance Analyst Intern. I have now joined the Sharks NRLW team as their Analyst for their inaugural season in the expanded NRLW competiton.

Experience

  • NRLW Analyst/NRL Analyst Intern - Cronulla Sharks
  • NRL Data Collection Agent - STATS Perform
  • Performance Analysis Intern - Football NSW Institute
  • Performance Analysis Intern - NSW Institute of Sport
  • Sports Analyst - TOPPA Sports

Education

Graduate Certificate in Data Analytics for Sport Performance

Victoria University

Bachelor of Applied Science (Exercise and Sport Science)

The University of Sydney
